OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1775596265
OL,3,CKnife crime 'hotspots' to be earmarked
OL,4,Cfor surge in policing
OL,6,FThe government has announced a #26
OL,7,Fmillion scheme to fund new ways to
OL,8,Fcrack down on knife crime in England
OL,9,Fand Wales.
OL,11,FThe scheme will include special 'hubs'
OL,12,Fto help guide young people away from
OL,13,Fcrime, and will fund the latest
OL,14,Fmapping technology to pinpoint knife
OL,15,Fcrime hot-spots.
OL,17,FPrecise mapping data will be used by
OL,18,Fpolice forces to help identify
OL,19,Fspecific specific streets and times
OL,20,Fwhen knife crime occurs most regularly.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
