OL,3,CKnife crime 'hotspots' to be earmarked
OL,4,Cfor surge in policing
OL,6,FThe Home Office announced that #26
OL,7,Fmillion will be put into a Knife Crime
OL,8,FConcentrations Fund, which will be
OL,9,Fallocated to the 27 police forces in
OL,10,FEngland and Wales that deal with 90%
OL,11,Fof knife crime.
OL,13,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,14,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,15,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,16,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
