OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1775596265
OL,3,CKnife crime 'hotspots' to be earmarked
OL,4,Cfor surge in policing
OL,6,FPolicing minister Sarah Jones said:
OL,7,F"Knife crime devastates lives and
OL,8,Ffamilies across the country, and the
OL,9,Fmajority of it takes place on just a
OL,10,Fsmall number of streets across the
OL,11,Fcountry.
OL,13,F"We will deploy state-of-the-art
OL,14,Fmapping to identify these hot spots
OL,15,Fand target them with police patrols,
OL,16,Flive facial recognition and knife
OL,17,Farches to catch these criminals.
OL,19,F"This Government will halve knife
OL,20,Fcrime within a decade, saving lives
OL,21,Fand protecting communities."
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOU{D@AOU}D@\O]
