CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1775596265
OL,3,CKnife crime 'hotspots' to be earmarked
OL,4,Cfor surge in policing
OL,6,FThe crackdown comes as part of a wider
OL,7,Fprogramme aimed at halving knife crime
OL,8,Fover a decade.
OL,10,FMinisters are also rolling out a new
OL,11,Fgeneration of youth centres as part of
OL,12,Fa plan called Protecting Lives,
OL,13,FBuilding Hope.
OL,15,FThe eight hubs will be based in
OL,16,FBirmingham, Brighton and Hove,
OL,17,FBristol, County Durham, Leeds,
OL,18,FManchester, Nottingham and Tower
OL,19,FHamlets, all areas with high rates of
OL,20,Fknife crime.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
